Mahalo is your guide to daily gratitude practice. In this update we have added a new Gratitude Journal page so that you can record and review all of your past completed practices. Upon completing a daily practice a new page is added to your journal. You can view the journal by tapping on a completed practice or by using the button on the Bonus Practices page. We are so excited for you to try it out! If you re enjoying using Mahalo please consider writing a review for us on the App Store. It really does help us a lot. We are just getting started here at Mahalo. If you have any feedback or suggestions please don t hesitate to reach out to us at contact freezegun.com. We can t wait to hear from you!

We have launched a brand new way to practice gratitude. Practicing gratitude should be easy to do and leave us feeling calm not stressed so the Mahalo team has created a new experience that improves on all aspects of the first version. You will be presented with new gratitude practices everyday that guide you through mediations affirmations reflections and so much more. Check out the new version of Mahalo and start practicing gratitude the easy way. We would love to hear your feedback you can reach out to us from Settings inside the app or via email at contact freezegun.com
